'''Cragus 12's bounty hunter armor''' was a unique suit of [[Armor/Legends|armor]] that belonged to the ruthless [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] [[Cragus 12]]. It was a full-body battle armor with a helmet that protected and concealed Cragus' head. The battle armor was equipped with a [[Jetpack/Legends|jet pack]] that had a movement range of 100 meters horizontally and 70 meters vertically as well as a [[Multi-Frequency Targeting and Acquisition System/Legends|Multi-Frequency Targeting and Acquisition System]]. Among other things, it also included a climate-controlled body glove, a self-contained air unit with two hours of oxygen, a built-in [[Comlink/Legends|comlink]] and a wrist laser.

